plot: Jax, Xander, Ralen, and Matta track Jax's Mother, Eve, and Tierney to a remote planet in uncharted space in the Horatius system. Upon arrival to Clayton's World, they discover one of the Ark ships, the Clayton, that was part of the Great Migration from Earth 150 years prior. While on the planet, they discover the descents of the original travelers, only to come in the crosshairs of their strange religious cult. The small group soon discovers that the cult will stop at nothing to maintain its sinister order. Meanwhile, back at Earthcom Fleet Training Academy on Earth, having been given a second chance at the academy, Jett starts to sew his wild oats, but ends up straining other relationships, especially with Zazie. Secrets are revealed by Eve and Jett.—whitetiger1206
